    {
      "id": 1,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "",
      "transparent": true,
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 4,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0
      },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "### ps-vector-memory\nThe background distillation goroutine in the **api** job: every five minutes it finds idle chat sessions, distills them into durable user facts via Anthropic, embeds them via OpenAI, and writes them to sqlite-vec. It **degrades silently** \u2014 if it stops, no request fails and nothing pages \u2014 so the top-left **Time since last successful sweep** tile is the one to watch; everything else explains _why_ it's behaving as it is. Sections: **Liveness & cadence** (is it running?) \u00b7 **Work done** (is it producing memories?) \u00b7 **Failures** (where is it breaking?) \u00b7 **Latency & cost** (how long, and how many tokens?). Hover any panel's title (\u24d8) for details and threshold meanings. Thresholds are starting proposals, trivially retunable."
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "type": "row",
      "title": "Liveness & cadence",
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 1,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 4
      },
      "panels": []
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Time since last successful sweep",
      "description": "THE headline tile: seconds since the goroutine last completed a sweep without a batch-level error (time() - max(api_vectormemory_last_success_timestamp_seconds)). At the five-minute cadence this should hover around a few hundred seconds. Warning at 720s (more than two missed ticks); critical at 1800s (30 min \u2014 the goroutine is effectively dead). This is the answer to \"is vector memory alive?\"",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 4,
        "w": 6,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 5
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus"
          },
          "expr": "time() - max(api_vectormemory_last_success_timestamp_seconds)",
          "refId": "A",
          "instant": true
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ],
          "fields": "",
          "values": false
        },
        "textMode": "value",
        "colorMode": "value",
        "graphMode": "area"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "s",
          "decimals": 0,
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": null
              },
              {
                "color": "yellow",
                "value": 720
              },
              {
                "color": "red",
                "value": 1800
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      }
    },
